Get $500 off your first month's rent when you sign by December 15! (Valid from 01/01/2024 till 01/31/2024)

Available 1/1/2024! $500 off 1st months' rent!! Welcome to your new Home! It includes 4 bed 2.5 bath open floor plan 1856sqft. Built in 2015 and located in a very quiet and desirable area of San Antonio. Nestled in Wolf Creek, quick access to 1604. Easy commute to Lackland, SeaWorld, and restaurants. This floor plan features an open kitchen with a view into the dining area and great room. From the moment you enter the family room is inviting and open from the second story with a metal rail staircase along the stairs, this is nothing short of AMAZING. The spacious floorplan and outdoor living spaces are perfect for entertaining guest. The master suite includes a bay window, and an exceptional master bath with separate tub and shower. Walk in closet. Ceramic tile can be seen in all wet areas. Complete with 2 wood faux blinds and garage door opener. Game room has been converted into a 4th bedroom complete with walk in closet. Home also includes -stove, microwave. Updated bath. Beautiful spacious backyard with wooden deck. Wake up in the deck each morning with no backyard neighbors. 2 car garage. Solar panels installed. Located in Bexar County with nearby schools including Big Country Elementary School, Francis R Scobee Middle School, and Southwest High School. Tenants are responsible for utilities, yard care, pest control, trash (1st 3 months FREE for trash service) and renters' insurance. Pets are on a case-by-case basis. $300 non-refundable per pet fee, $25 per pet monthly rent. Deposit $1,990. Rent is due on the 1st. Late Fees apply after the 3rd. $35 a day. HOA $30 monthly.

Renter responsible for utilities and trash. Pet deposit required for all pets.

Tenants is responsible to pay for water, electricity (utilities), trash (1st 3 months FREE for trash service), yard care, pest control and renters' insurance. No smoking allowed inside the home. Pets are on a case-by-case basis. $300 non-refundable per pet fee, $25 per pet monthly rent. Deposit $1990. $500 off 1st months' rent. Rent is due on the 1st. Late Fees apply after the 3rd. $35 a day.
